696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ciara-and-kesha-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ciara-and-kesha-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kesha">Kesha</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ciara">Ciara</a>已被宣布为 2025 年 Mighty Hoopla 音乐节的主角。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/mighty-hoopla-camp-festivals-3582771">为什么我们不能失去像 Mighty Hoopla 这样的假日营节日周末者</a></strong></li></ul><p>明年伦敦音乐节的阵容中还宣布了一系列其他名字，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kate-nash">Kate Nash</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixie-lott">Pixie Lott</a> 、Loreen、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vengaboys">Vengaboys</a> 、Mutya、Jamelia、Jojo、Erika Jayne、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/g-flip">G Flip</a>和 Daniel Bedingfield 等。</p><p>明年的活动将于 2025 年 5 月 31 日至 6 月 1 日在伦敦布罗克韦尔公园举行。席亚拉 (Ciara) 将于周六 (31) 成为头条新闻，凯莎 (Kesha) 将于周日 (1) 登台。</p><p>现在可以从<a href="https://mightyhoopla.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>购买 Mighty Hoopla 的周末和日票。</p><p>在下面的海报上查看到目前为止的完整阵容。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBYdD8zi-J7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 